BallCatcher v1.0
-------------------
1) To use the program, unzip the archive file.
2) Double-click on BallCatcher.exe

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------
- You must own two PS3 Eye cameras
- You must have purchased the "CL PS3 Eye Driver" and "CL PS3 Eye Multicam SDK"
- You must have activated the webcams from the CL Multicam device manager by purchasing credits from CL (Code Laboratories)

TROUBLESHOOTING
-------------------
If you get an error regarding the Visual Studio 14
C++ redistributables, you may download those files from:
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=48145